### Ingress Backend API Test Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or copy to Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Register Another User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login Another User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User Profile (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Fund Wallet (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/fund-wallet
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send HBAR to User's Wallet
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/send-hbar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": "10"
}

### Transfer HBAR to Another Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/transfer-hbar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccountId": "0.0.12345",
  "amount": "5"
}

### Get Wallet Balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/wallet-balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test Invalid Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Test Missing Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### Test Wrong Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Test No Token (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Test Invalid Token (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here


